observations.recommendation:
We recommended that Management instruct the Municipal Accountant and responsible officers to:

Immediately seek legal remedies to settle/collect the long overdue receivables particularly the SEAP;

Continue monitoring and visiting those delinquent borrowers and issue Demand Letters to ensure the recovery and realization of the receivables; 

Immediately determine and evaluate those borrowers who are deceased and unknown/missing in accordance with COA Circular No. 2016-005 and prepare requests for write-off if collections are already remote; and 

Make an immediate representation and reconciliation of the un-reconciled items with the Provincial Treasury.

